snippet.title: Super Sonic Knockout 2011 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit the game's blog-site @ http://www.supersonicknockout.x10.mx/

Facebook Page @ http://www.facebook.com/SuperSonicKnockout

This is it. Super Sonic Knockout is finally getting a new demo after so long, and it's coming out tomorrow as part of the SAGE 2011 event. The project is a week from being 6 years old and it's only getting stronger!
